                "storage": {
                    "value": "<h1>System Overview</h1><p>The Energy Optimization Platform v2 is designed to handle millions of IoT events per minute from our solar and wind installations in the US. It uses Kafka for ingestion, Apache Flink for real-time processing, and stores aggregated metrics in TimescaleDB.</p><h2>Key Components</h2><ul><li><strong>Ingestion Gateway:</strong> Normalizes payloads from different turbine models.</li><li><strong>Prediction Engine:</strong> Uses ML to predict generation based on weather forecasts.</li></ul>",
